{
  "stem": "5639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And indeed, she worked in the kitchen until she was replaced by somebody younger, by another commandant, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I stayed in Bedzin till after June '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that because our contact with the outside world became very limited, and the only contact-- official contact-- was when we were allowed take the rubbish out to a rubbish dump outside the town.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to be escorted that by the guards, push the barrel [POINTS] with the rubbish in the middle of the roads, guards on two sides of the barrel, and we went to the rubbish dump.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And over there was Polish workers, and they approached me and they said, the invasion has started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what the invasion is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a completely apolitical animal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came back, and I told them the wonderful news.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Look, I've got a limited time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't dwell on any other episode, which important as it might be and significant as it is, can't fit in to one hour.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it must have been soon after the invasion, triggered off by escape of two children which I have also arranged.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were sent out--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My niece-- my cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my cousin I put in care of a Polish woman. 10 days or a week before the Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her parents would have been alive, perhaps, if they wouldn't have gone, on Saturday, home to do some washing and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- not only my aunt, but generally, parents were very, very reluctant to part with the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Although as you and many other interviewers cannot comprehend how come that they still did not know what's happening?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not afford to absorb the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just could not.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
